column8: The Horn of Plenty which you bear once overflowed. It holds a certain power still, of course. But never again shall mortalkind take it for granted.
No comfort from the bitter cold!
Shiver and rot, for all I care!
I have no tolerance for disrespect.
I warned you not to side against me, little sprout.
Respect your elders next time, Zagreus.

Why, it appears you wield Varatha's form known as the Frost Fair Blade! So then it's travelled that much farther than I thought. Make swift use of its power, Zagreus; it may soon leave you as the seasons do.
My greetings to you, little sprout.
You staying warm of late, young Zagreus?
A winter's greeting to you, Zagreus.
That's not a problem, little sprout.
I've something for you, little sprout.
I have a gift for you, young Zagreus.
A simple oversight is all it was.
That was most certainly in error, Zagreus.
You oughtn't test my patience, little sprout.
That was an eminently foolish choice.
I'm very proud of you, young Zagreus.
